data.title: 205 West Louisiana Street suite 103, McKinney, TX, USA
data.meta_description: Aggressive representation to secure what you love most. Mary Neal Family Law, PLLC is your go-to Collin County child custody attorney.
data.text:
Mary Neal represented me in a custody modification over the past two years. Throughout such a trying time full of twists and turns, Mary handled my case with grace. She has been the most ethical attorney I’ve come into contact with & is the only one I would trust. I highly recommend her to anyone needing family law help!

​

- Chelsea S., former client

I can’t express enough gratitude for the extraordinary legal representation I received from Mary Neal during my divorce and custody dispute over the last two years. Mary handled every aspect of my complex case with brilliance and integrity. She is not only an exceptional attorney, with immense expertise in family law and custody litigation, but she also genuinely cares about and listens to her clients. She was a constant support and gave invaluable advice and reassurance at the many twists and turns of the case. She is honest, ethical, and has tons of integrity. Mary’s paralegal, Melanie Carter, was also amazing and provided impeccable assistance throughout the process. Thank you for everything Mary and Melanie!

​

- Jonas H., former client
